<messaging:emailTemplate subject="Participant Notification for Fixed Price DTW Incentive Projects" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ParticipantAcknowledgement__c">
<messaging:htmlEmailBody >
    <apex:outputpanel >
        <p>Congratulations!  You have been selected to participate in the <b><i>Deliver to Win Fixed Price Incentive Plan</i></b>, 
        which is a project specific incentive plan designed to drive improvement in project delivery, including financial and operational results such as safety, 
        client satisfaction and cash collection, and to reward strong team performance in these areas.</p>
        
        <p>Project Number: {!relatedTo.ProjectNumber__c} </p>
        <p>Project Name: {!relatedTo.ProjectName__c}</p>
        <p>Customer Name: {!relatedTo.ClientName__c}</p>
        
        <p>Your personalized enrollment letter is attached, which includes project specific metrics and an overview of the plan.  
        Please review this enrollment letter, and click the &nbsp;<apex:outputtext escape="false" value="{!relatedTo.AcknowledgementURL__c}" />   
        within 7 days to indicate your receipt and participation in the plan.</p>
        
        <p>Please review the &nbsp;<apex:outputtext escape="false" value="{!relatedTo.DTWFixedPricePlanEmployeeGuide__c}" /> and complete the Overview and Participant modules of our DTW Fixed Price Training to learn more about the incentive plan, 
        and how you can earn a cash reward.  Training should take roughly 45 minutes to complete.  In addition to the web-based training, more information and other resources can be found on the 
         &nbsp;<apex:outputtext escape="false" value="{!relatedTo.DTWWebpage__c}" /> webpage.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you, </p>
        
        <p>DTW Administrator</p>
        <p>{!relatedTo.ParticipantID__r.EnrollmentPlan__r.ReplyTo__c}</p>
    </apex:outputpanel>
</messaging:htmlEmailBody>
    
    <messaging:plainTextEmailBody >
        Congratulations! You have been selected to participate in the Deliver to Win Fixed Price Incentive Plan, which is a project specific incentive plan designed to drive improvement in project delivery, including financial and operational results such as safety, client satisfaction and cash collection, and to reward strong team performance in these areas. 
        
        Project Number: {!relatedTo.ProjectNumber__c} 
        
        Project Name: {!relatedTo.ProjectName__c} 
        
        Customer Name: {!relatedTo.ClientName__c} 
        
        Your personalized enrollment letter is attached, which includes project specific metrics and an overview of the plan.  Please review this enrollment letter, and click the Participant Acknowledgement within 7 days to indicate your receipt and participation in the plan. 
        
        Please review {!relatedTo.DTWFixedPricePlanEmployeeGuideURL__c} and complete the Overview and Participant modules of our DTW Fixed Price Training to learn more about the incentive plan, and how you can earn a cash reward. Training should take roughly 45 minutes to complete. In addition to the web-based training, more information and other resources can be found at {!relatedTo.DTWWebpageURL__c}.         
        
        Thank you, 
        
        DTW Administrator    
        
        {!relatedTo.ParticipantID__r.EnrollmentPlan__r.ReplyTo__c}
    </messaging:plainTextEmailBody>      

<messaging:attachment renderAs="PDF" filename="{!relatedTo.ProjectNumber__c}-{!relatedTo.ParticipantID__r.EmployeeName__r.name}-DTWLetter-{!YEAR(TODAY())}{!RIGHT(TEXT(MONTH(TODAY())+100),2)}{!RIGHT(TEXT(DAY(TODAY())+100),2)}.pdf">
    <c:INC_EnrollmentLetterComponent EP="{!relatedTo.ParticipantID__c}" pa="{!relatedTo}" />
</messaging:attachment>
</messaging:emailTemplate>